name: Brain Symphony: Relax & Meditation
summary:
Brain Symphony – Your Sanctuary in VR

Step into four beautifully crafted Realms designed to help you relax, breathe, and find emotional balance. Each Realm offers immersive scenes, guided meditations, calming audio, and interactive elements that respond to your presence. Just put on your headset and feel the change begin.  

Cosmic Realm – Explore Luminous Space

Travel through glowing auroras, the Milky Way, and other cosmic worlds that shimmer and move with your breath. Enjoy soothing sleep spaces,...
